<h2 id="toc5"><span><strong>TERMINATION ORDER FOR THE ABOVE</strong></span></h2>
<blockquote>
<p>Dr. Rights, as one of her first assignments, asks for the permission to terminate the last of them when it becomes too violent and unstable to risk keeping around, and nothing more can be learned from it. &quot;There will always be other monster out there. But you're a special kind of fucked.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>

